metadata.name: Mary Jane #bboo2
metadata.description:
Herb wind and fire together at last,

Causing a reaction, ever so fast.

No obstructions to limit the receptors receiving

The sudden rushing wave, the dopamine feeling.

But now Tony’s different, he’ll never be the same.

He’s changed his hair, his gender, and even his name.

Away into the disco forest, walking in slow-mo.

Now walks Tary, dressed in drag queen camo.
